{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dca53a70ad","title":"复彭雪枫电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"110ea7342a","index":0,"year":1941,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"dca53a70ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2c39662e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"复彭雪枫电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"dca53a70ad"},{"id":"8dd9c0b44b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年6月28日）你五月三日电的观点是不适当的，是错误的，六月十五日电办还未改变。蒋介石还在抗战，蒋在全国军队中，在中产阶级及小资产阶级中，还有很大信仰，目前抗战还少不了他，他也还没有破裂统一战线，他还是两面政策。黑工黑课的策略只能使自己陷于孤立，八路南下的策略也只能加深国共裂痕，与中央缩小裂痕的方针是不合的。我们对付蒋介石反共政策的方针只应该是有理、有利、有节的自卫政策，你的意见却超越这个方针。在苏德战争爆发后，我党对国民党态度尤须慎重，不可大意","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"dca53a70ad"}],"page":{"id":"a1c653dd35","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"dca53a70ad","start":145,"end":145}}}},"__N_SSG":true}